## Nommage

| Élément | Convention | Exemple |
|---|---|---|
| Composant | PascalCase | `ServiceCard.tsx` |
| Hook custom | camelCase préfixé `use` | `useScrollReveal.ts` |
| Util | camelCase | `formatDate.ts` |
| Constante | SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE | `SERVICES`, `NAV_ITEMS` |
| Type/Interface | PascalCase | `ServiceCardProps` |
| Handler | `handle` + action | `handleSubmitForm` |
